# Cyclic maintenance logic

## Single source of truth

All cyclic preventive status logic **must** go through:

- `lib/maintenance/due-engine.ts` — `buildDueLedger()`, `previewCheckpointAbsorption()`
- `lib/utils/cyclic-maintenance.ts` — `computeCyclicIntervalResults()` (adapter), `computeCyclicIntervalResultsForAsset()` (dual-meter)

**Do not** add cycle-slice filters, category gates, tier windows, or duplicate engines in pages or API routes.

Full contract: `docs/CYCLIC_MAINTENANCE_SOURCE_OF_TRUTH.md`

## Checkpoint invariant

A preventive completion is a **checkpoint**: it settles all unpaid dues ≤ its meter. Only dues **after** the latest preventive meter can be `overdue`.

## Policies

- **P1:** `maintenance_category` — display only, never coverage
- **P2:** Absorption recorded in `maintenance_history.absorbed_services`; preview in completion form
- **P3:** `both` models — split intervals by type in `lib/maintenance/dual-meter.ts`

## Callers (use adapter only)

- Asset detail, mantenimiento tab, nuevo WO, assets list, calendar, reports API, alerts edge fn, production report, composite dashboard

## Debug

- `?debugCycles=1` on mantenimiento page
- Fleet diagnostics: `/gestion/mantenimiento/diagnosticos`

## Tests

Run `npm run test:unit` after any engine or adapter change. BP-01 replay must stay green.
